{"tid":1822253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加菲貓太黃被封殺","createTime":"2020-01-12T23:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T23:42:12.000Z","uid":297241,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e662fbc950bf62f687d2389165959956f3cd5ec","tid":1822253,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T23:35:04.000Z","msg":"替北京過濾敏感資訊　綠壩鬧笑話<br />\n加菲貓太黃被封殺<br />\n<br />\n「我想看加菲貓，可是被過濾掉了；黑人的裸體圖像，卻蒙混過關！」內地針對色情及敏感資訊、將於下月強制使用的過濾軟件「綠壩─花季護航」，鬧出笑話。內地一名網絡從業員試用該軟件後發現，加菲貓和黃牛因顏色太黃被過濾掉，黑人裸體圖像卻成功過關。他又批評該過濾軟件將上網資料全程記錄，私隱安全備受威脅。"},{"pid":"058469dfab75fa758fceaea3191bd4819b67b0af","tid":1822253,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"將來黃種人太黃，封哂所有黃種人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">台灣就公投完啦 甘香港人呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n一人一票<span style=\"color: red;\"> 香</span><span style=\"color: green;\">港</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">地</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">投</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">票</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港地投票 ~ 一個香港人的投票應用程式</span><br />\n下載連結：iOS / Android<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=e6743556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org</a><br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1</a>"}]}